snippet.title: Super Mario and the Monstrous Manor - SM64 Romhack Release & Download
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more romhacks in the future: https://www.youtube.com/c/MrComit?sub_confirmation=1

Download it here: https://romhacking.com/hack/super-mario-and-the-monstrous-manor

My biggest hack yet is finally here! I got the idea to make this hack almost 4 years ago, and since then I've been carefully crafting a mod that would push my skills in 3d modelling, coding, story writing, music composition, and of course game design - all while having a structure that is unlike any large mario 64 romhack out there. I am so excited for you to finally play it, and I hope you enjoy :)

Github Repo: https://github.com/MrComit/smmm
